=== Test/http://rdfa.info/test-suite/test-cases/rdfa1.1/xhtml1/manifest#0261

encodingtest.TripleStatementList{
	{
		Triple: rdf.Triple{
			Subject: rdf.IRI("http://www.example.org"),

				LexicalForm: "This is\nan XMLLiteral",

			},
